name: User-list
body:
### Welcome to BVP LUG
This is the list of users registered with the Linux User Group of Bharati Vidyapeeth's College Of Engineering. To register, all you need to do is make changes to this repository and create a pull request [here](https://github.com/BVPLUG/User-List)
tagline: List of users registered with Linux User Group of Bharati Vidyapeeth's College Of Engineering
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
